    <section>
      <title>Drawings</title>

      <para>As far as possible, drawings supplied with this manual are
      incorporated into the body of the text, however some large or
      third-party drawings are inserted in the annexes.</para>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Manufacturer's manuals</title>

      <para>The manuals of the equipment supplied with the ship are bundled
      and supplied together with this manual and are considered to form an
      integral part of it. For a list of supplied manufacturer's manuals see
      <xref linkend="bibliography"/>. Reference to manufacturer manuals in
      text is often accompanied by the symbol <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata contentwidth="0.5cm"
                       fileref="resources/images/DIN_4844-2/mandatory/M018_read_manual.svg"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject>.</para>

      <para><inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata contentwidth="0.5cm"
                       fileref="resources/images/DIN_4844-2/warning/W000_general.svg"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject>The text of manufacturer supplied manuals always
      prevails over the text in this owner's manual.</para>
